<h1 style="background-color:#eee;float:left;padding:10px;width:270px;height:550px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:20px;display:inline-block">Wordly game!</h1>
<p style="color:#888;float:left;">Do you want to play some super amazing, perfect, incredible WORDLY game?</p>
<br><br>
<%= link_to "Start GAME" , check_word_path %>
<br>

<div style="white-space:pre">
    <b>HOW TO PLAY</b>

    Guess the correct word in 6 tries.

    Each guess must be a valid 5 letter word
    with non repeating letters.

    After a guess, the tile colors will change to
    show how close your guess was to the word.


    <span style="background-color:#ddd;"> A </span> - Not in the word in any spot

    <span style="background-color:#fef9cc;"> A </span> - In the word but in the wrong spot

    <span style="background-color:#ccfecf;"> A </span> - in the word and in the correct spot
</div>

<pre>
<br>
<b> Next Puzzle: </b><%= @time_till_next_game%>
<br>
</pre>